# PHP features to add which behave in special ways:

## Keyword blocks:
- function
- switch, case
- if, else, elseif
- do, loop, while, for, foreach
- array(1,2,3)
- array(a => b. c => d)

## language syntax:
- [new, style, arrays]
- [new => style, arrays=>like_this]

# phplint features:

- options to parser from command line.
- colourful output
- test suite
- documentation
- warnings about similar words & variables
- including other files.
